<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0971009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0971009">（宋）＋西【明】</note>
<note n="0972001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0972001">愛＝受【三】</note>
<note n="0972002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0972002">善＝得【元】</note>
<note n="0972003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0972003">囉＝羅【三】</note>
<note n="0972004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0972004">虔＝犍【明】＊</note>
<note n="0972005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0972005">裝＝莊【三】＊</note>
<note n="0973001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0973001">悲＝非【元】，作【明】</note>
<note n="0973002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0973002">我＝宮【元】</note>
